Package com.atlan.model.fields

Class NumericRankField

java.lang.Object
com.atlan.model.fields.AtlanField
com.atlan.model.fields.SearchableField
com.atlan.model.fields.NumericRankField
All Implemented Interfaces:
INumericallySearchable, IRankSearchable, ISearchable
public class NumericRankField extends SearchableField implements INumericallySearchable, IRankSearchable
Represents any field in Atlan that can be searched using only numeric search operations, but also has a rank-orderable index.
